dct_title_s: Plat showing surveys of portions of lands of LSJU lying within the limites of the Town of Mayfield. Surveyed at the request of the Town Board of Trustees. Surveyed Oct. 1-4, 1918, by W. H. Myrick
dct_description_sm: Shows area bound by El Camino, Lincoln (California Ave?), Yale Street in what is now College Terrace area. Removed from SC027, box 13, folder 20.
dct_rights_sm: Property rights reside with the repository. Literary rights reside with  the creators of the documents or their heirs. To obtain permission to publish or reproduce, please contact the Public Services Librarian of the Dept. of Special Collections (http://library.stanford.edu/spc).
